{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WakeLockSentinel: release イベント","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WakeLockSentinel/release_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen_Wake_Lock_API\">Screen Wake Lock API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>インターフェイス</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WakeLock\"><code>WakeLock</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WakeLockSentinel\"><code>WakeLockSentinel</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/wakelock\"><code>Navigator.wakelock</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>安全なコンテキスト用:</strong> この機能は一部またはすべての<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">対応しているブラウザー</a>において、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">安全なコンテキスト</a> (HTTPS) でのみ利用できます。</p></div>\n<p><strong><code>release</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WakeLockSentinel\"><code>WakeLockSentinel</code></a> インターフェイスのイベントで、この見張りオブジェクトのハンドルが解放されたときに発行されます。</p>\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WakeLockSentinel\"><code>WakeLockSentinel</code></a> は <code>release()</code> メソッドにより手動で解放したり、プラットフォームの起動ロックにより自動的に解放されたりします。これは、文書がアクティブでなくなった場合や、見えなくなった場合、端末の電力が低下した場合、ユーザーが省電力モードをオンにした場合に発生する可能性があります。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<p>このイベント名を <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a> などで用いるか、イベントハンドラープロパティを設定するかしてください。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'release'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">onrelease</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"イベント型","title":"イベント型","isH3":false,"content":"<p>一般的な <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>この例では、起動ロックが解放されたときに UI を更新します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>wakeLock<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'release'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// if wake lock is released alter the UI accordingly</span>\n  statusElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Wake Lock has been released'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/screen-wake-lock/#the-onrelease-attribute","title":"Screen Wake Lock API"}],"query":"api.WakeLockSentinel.release_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.WakeLockSentinel.release_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WakeLockSentinel/release_event/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"イベント型","id":"イベント型"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"release は WakeLockSentinel インターフェイスのイベントで、この見張りオブジェクトのハンドルが解放されたときに発行されます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WakeLockSentinel: release event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/wakelocksentinel/release_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/wakelocksentinel/release_event/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WakeLockSentinel","title":"WakeLockSentinel"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WakeLockSentinel/release_event","title":"WakeLockSentinel: release イベント"}],"pageTitle":"WakeLockSentinel: release イベント - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}